{"tid":1841771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】初一「獨市」　旺角藥房驚現1400元一盒 N95醫護口罩","createTime":"2020-01-25T11:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T02:33:19.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3892cf6fb0b99b793bf5c4df0dfbb0c652584608","tid":1841771,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】初一「獨市」 旺角藥房驚現1400元一盒 N95醫護口罩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3915416/org/964a9dc73af8b0c37fd48a3e1b8b714f.jpg/E_gjpZE69DQN4JWc5y2Q1b1CxG_s5vDDoFqk4aBapOE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3915416%2Forg%2F964a9dc73af8b0c37fd48a3e1b8b714f.jpg%2FE_gjpZE69DQN4JWc5y2Q1b1CxG_s5vDDoFqk4aBapOE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=9a42b123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3915292/org/be932b4f9ec09a90033309c92030b6ec.jpg/CimxbvajNrDA9WSMFhlvKD1v1Ly6dbnIVNX0vn7V9L4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3915292%2Forg%2Fbe932b4f9ec09a90033309c92030b6ec.jpg%2FCimxbvajNrDA9WSMFhlvKD1v1Ly6dbnIVNX0vn7V9L4&h=82726d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3915300/org/1c6351b89da0dbb42a718ff12a81e25f.jpg/_ZQLb_-CKoJbwYZq-ZZ-3UiosGqKDjIoSetYf2PrWH8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3915300%2Forg%2F1c6351b89da0dbb42a718ff12a81e25f.jpg%2F_ZQLb_-CKoJbwYZq-ZZ-3UiosGqKDjIoSetYf2PrWH8&h=7a9bb7bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3915299/org/74cc13750c8572a5a911b30b9bc09160.jpg/1YjsyywjKu6L83AqObx6U-aMW4P3rg0AjImFpKaJhaQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3915299%2Forg%2F74cc13750c8572a5a911b30b9bc09160.jpg%2F1YjsyywjKu6L83AqObx6U-aMW4P3rg0AjImFpKaJhaQ&h=3894ad38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3915298/org/a93adc216a88732147a8ad694eadf8eb.jpg/Gkxpwzx5dYtsiQGb-2XsNeuo_3Phyr7gKkoAdgBKAHY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3915298%2Forg%2Fa93adc216a88732147a8ad694eadf8eb.jpg%2FGkxpwzx5dYtsiQGb-2XsNeuo_3Phyr7gKkoAdgBKAHY&h=e5a7b51e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3915294/org/b3cff478b103df4fc449127592adf150.jpg/_89yOd0rfTd4ET3PUIte6r1oJUqvhTqrK6z9OwGs_Ts\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3915294%2Forg%2Fb3cff478b103df4fc449127592adf150.jpg%2F_89yOd0rfTd4ET3PUIte6r1oJUqvhTqrK6z9OwGs_Ts&h=c7148446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3915293/org/ac02cbef648c487158eb44218809bcd6.jpg/ZazU4kjxte41m3I756RAuWGrDhx1hY3ISuZkKGDmZCg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3915293%2Forg%2Fac02cbef648c487158eb44218809bcd6.jpg%2FZazU4kjxte41m3I756RAuWGrDhx1hY3ISuZkKGDmZCg&h=dd75a4bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3915297/org/a63b05c54c915c13970815ca709d335c.jpg/9fnfu9bSr8mcoTXAudjpJhqa3b8bgpDH9wWOVd0FjlU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3915297%2Forg%2Fa63b05c54c915c13970815ca709d335c.jpg%2F9fnfu9bSr8mcoTXAudjpJhqa3b8bgpDH9wWOVd0FjlU&h=f580c9b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情在中國大陸持續擴大，全球確診病例增至1,287宗，41人死亡，香港至今已錄得5宗確診個案。由於武漢肺炎確定會人傳人，不少香港市民出入公共場所，都會戴上口罩自保。<br />\n<br />\n雖然今日(25日)是年初一，但在武漢肺炎肆虐的情況下，旺角區一帶有藥房仍照常營業，店舖當眼處更擺放各類口罩。有藥房更將防護級別較高的1860型號的N95口罩，標價80元一個，1400元一盒，惟記者觀察附近藥房都沒有同型號口罩出售，該藥房亦可算是「獨市生意」。<br />\n<br />\n旺角旺區一帶藥房，不少均年初一照常營業，店舖當眼處擺放各類口罩，售價由58元至1400元<br />\n過往年初一，不少店舖均會收爐賀新春，惟今年武漢肺炎直迫香港，社區人心惶惶。記者今日（25日）中午到旺角通菜街及花園街一帶視察，大部分藥房均已啟市，店舖的當眼處，更擺放各式各類的口罩售賣，當中有防護能力較強的N95口罩、成人外科口罩、醫護用手術口罩及兒童口罩等。每盒平均價格由58元至1400元不等。<br />\n<br />\n其中在西洋菜南街，一間連鎖藥房當眼位置，除出擺放一般成人外科口罩外，亦有出售屬醫護級防護口罩1860型號的N95口罩，藥房標價80元一個，每盒則售價1400元。惟記者見附近藥房都沒有售賣同型號口罩，該藥房亦可算是「獨市生意」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3915302/org/f0f0434862dd9593aa1524404f973214.jpg/bMi6YfInokVf0QBiVzG7AAA0k1e2_9jE-UcwaNNHMGg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3915302%2Forg%2Ff0f0434862dd9593aa1524404f973214.jpg%2FbMi6YfInokVf0QBiVzG7AAA0k1e2_9jE-UcwaNNHMGg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=6722d612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有在本港工作的內地人，今日亦到旺角的藥房大手購入10盒售價138元的口罩自用。（張美華攝）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其中一間藥房職員透露，由於近日武漢肺炎疫情加劇，口罩供應緊張，「原本都冇貨賣，但老細好難先買到番嚟。」對於近日市面上有來歷不明，甚至假口罩出現，職員坦言：「其實而家都唔知㗎喇，有貨就入啦，日本台灣嗰啲就一定貴啲」又指自己目前使用的，是較早購入的台灣口罩，又謂藥房今日口罩銷情仍然良好。<br />\n<br />\n本港工作內地人一次過購入10盒 4層的口罩<br />\n<br />\n有在本港工作的內地人，今日亦到旺角的藥房大手購入10盒售價138元的口罩自用。他表示，今日見旺角藥房有營業，便四處格價，見有聲稱4層的口罩賣138元，便購入10盒。問及市面有假口罩湧現，他則表示「都冇辦法㗎喇，都唔知真假，有就買咗先，好過冇」。"},{"pid":"e98278a1612952778f08e2cc2e2d02a97545fe8f","tid":1841771,"uid":72228,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:30:45.000Z","msg":"岩架啦 支那人比翻藥房支那狗呃錢"},{"pid":"8f41f479e6256f3afd4f3bf93924e33c00912dfb","tid":1841771,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:31:03.000Z","msg":"一定要清算哩班發人血財嘅仆街"},{"pid":"a322e8b161a66176d092d5f921d3f07d33a347e7","tid":1841771,"uid":188685,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:31:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">醫護罷工</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.29抗疫三罷<br />\n每日消毒手機眼鏡</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1XGsCe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1XGsCe.jpg&h=233e7882&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/inpQ5oV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FinpQ5oV.jpg&h=80136c07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TP6TiLj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3